程序包 com.rfid

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ReaderConnector
    The implementation class of ModuleConnector to manager FRID reader connector.
    ReaderDataPackageParser
    The implementation class of DataPackageParser.You can resolve the return data by RFID.
    ReaderDataPackageProcess
    The implementation class of DataPackageProcess.You can process the data package return by RFID reader.And DataPackageProcess is an #Observable,it will send data package to #RXObserver.So the client can receive the processed data by override the according method in #RXObserver.Before you must register it to #RFIDReaderHelper subclass.
    RFIDReaderHelper
    The core class to operate RFIDreader.You can send command to RFID reader via the methods.
